  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >General</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334590/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325255\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><strong>Furry Love </strong>is an <strong>Entertaining Arcade Game</strong>, consisting of <strong>a Series of Exciting Mini-Games</strong> with the <strong>Attractive Furry Girls</strong> 🐺<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334590/extras/be62dcd3a65ac2a973417964cb236473.avif?t=1725325255\" width=587 height=206 /></span><br><strong>Beautiful Furry Girls</strong>, <strong>Amazing Atmosphere</strong>,<strong> Great Music</strong>, <strong>32 Levels with Full HD Furry Artworks</strong>.<br>Great for <strong>relaxing </strong>after a hard day at work. <strong>Join us</strong>! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334590/extras/4d8ad6000c5203042de5ba23749acc1d.webp?t=1725325255\" width=36 height=28 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334590/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325255\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Five Unique Game Modes</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334590/extras/9ffba4be86c27203991c4f0b5e670183.webp?t=1725325255\" width=36 height=28 /></span><br></li><li><strong>Dynamic Gameplay</strong> and <strong>Various Difficulty</strong> Levels <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1334590/extras/278d597d18afd4aa0750c1200137f6a2.webp?t=1725325255\" wi